        "timestamp": "2023-02-09 14:22:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nCan you check if this tool breaks, Francesco?  https://git.onap.org/policy/drools-pdp/tree/policy-management/src/main/server-gen/bin/telemetry (as it goes by the swagger spec).",
