          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2023-02-09 15:24:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> > Patch Set 2:\n> > \n> > Can you check if this tool breaks, Francesco?  https://git.onap.org/policy/drools-pdp/tree/policy-management/src/main/server-gen/bin/telemetry (as it goes by the swagger spec).\n> \n> Hi Jorge, it does break. Since the /swagger.json endpoint it's nulled. What do you suggest?\n> \n> /opt/app/policy/bin $ sh policy --debug start\n>   L []: Policy Management (pid 270) is running'\n>   L []: Policy Management (pid 270) is running\n> /opt/app/policy/bin $ sh telemetry \n>   sh: true: unknown operand\n>   generating new spec ..\n>   error: cannot generate telemetry spec\n\nquestion, is there an url that can generate the swagger spec?\n could point script to that url instead for the tool to get the spec",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "18c7f1b74819709269f965805cdb5d5d3e6e17b4",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 7629,
