          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2023-02-09 18:02:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> > question, is there an url that can generate the swagger spec?\n> \n> \n> At the moment there is no endpoint. In the other spring projects we used spring-doc that creates /v3/api-docs endpoint.\n> \n> In this case, during the build a swagger.json file is generated in target/generated-sources/swagger/swagger.json I could add an endpoint GET /swagger to retrieve this document, and change the endpoint in the telemetry tool.\n\nthat would be great, that may solve it.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
