        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Jorge, I added the endpoint http://{DROOLS_IP}:9696/policy/pdp/engine/swagger\nThe content is the json file being generated in /target/generated-sources/ and copied in src/main/resources.\n\nI tested the telemetry tool in Docker and it works fine\n/opt/app/policy/bin $ sh telemetry \ngenerating new spec ..\nVersion: 2.1.0\nhttp://localhost:9696/policy/pdp/engine> exit\nGoodbye!\n\nThe old endpoint (implemented in policy-common) http://{DROOLS_IP}:9696/swagger.json produces an empty json as expected",
